name: EMPTY WORLD (VisedFeline121)
description:
The title says is all! 

In this short game('s demo) you can empty the world!

Can you pass past the mighty rolloc make it to the end? (probably!)

This is pretty much my first game (and trijam), it's not really a game per se, more like testing a concept and making something by myself, but I had fun making it so it's OK :)

Controls are WASD to move and SPACE to empty that world.
